column2: "The spectral FDR used were 0.01 at the spectral level; 0.01 at the peptide level; and 0.01 at the protein level."
"An MSGFDB_SpecEValue below 3.9297e-10 has to be utilized."
"Using this MSGF_SpecProb cutoff resulted in 4583 spectra conserved; 4439 peptides identified; and 1596 proteins identified with at least 1 unique peptide(s)."
"The final FDR were the following : Spectral FDR=0.00360766629086809; Peptide FDR=0.00372699743768926; and Protein FDR=0.00999375390381012."
